title: GitHub: Create branch and commit changes

cells.data:
1. Go to Branches and click + sign, enter name, click Branch
2. Do work in branch

**To work in other branch click checkmark to left of branch

3. When ready to publish, click Merge View (top-right)
4. Drag in to and from
5. Click Merge Branches

I THINK Â SOME THINGS HAVE TO BE DONE ON GITHUB.COM FOR THIS TO WORK


6. From down arrow in branch one can delete branch
